Question: No image contains more than three fragrance bottles, and each image includes at least one squarish bottle.

Reference Answer: True

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many fragrance bottles are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many fragrance bottles are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} <= 3 and {ANSWER1} <= 3')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there at least one squarish bottle in the image?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there at least one squarish bottle in the image?')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER5} and {ANSWER6}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER7)
```
